{"tid":2014171,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"賴弘國受訪後突喊「汶川大地震」 網友:???","createTime":"2020-05-13T00:06:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-13T06:15:10.000Z","uid":41343,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"7b2051157ed50838c8b6b87036222fc9afd4fa54","tid":2014171,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T00:06:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://stars.udn.com/star/story/10091/4557543\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstars.udn.com%2Fstar%2Fstory%2F10091%2F4557543&d=RJ6DAKdT%2BAkj0rfdhPz9NR6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=a3af6273\" target=\"_blank\">https://stars.udn.com/star/story/10091/4557543</a><br />\n<br />\n賴弘國復工首度現身談阿嬌婚變，談及婚姻，他提出五點聲明，希望大家給他們一點空間，被問及是否為轉移周揚戀焦點，他則說「不回應」，但強調網路毀謗者，一定會告死對方。<br />\n<br />\n不過賴弘國受訪完以後，像是想到什麼後回頭說：「今天是汶川大地震12周年祭，我希望亡者已矣，逝者如斯，謝謝大家。」引起網友全困惑，還有網友糾正說原文並非為「逝者如斯」，而是「生者如斯」、對於他臨時的發文倍感困惑。"},{"pid":"52224364b493edeedc08d854f585d09d48e6912b","tid":2014171,"uid":4709,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T00:10:10.000Z","msg":"佢痴Q左線呀"},{"pid":"805cd918389549a4664ad5a5d80f6689f2dd56e0","tid":2014171,"uid":2914,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T00:10:44.000Z","msg":"精神病會傳染<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d7ad7e7d17f334da32b201fbf657113f087d20e","tid":2014171,"uid":317378,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T00:11:56.000Z","msg":"祝福黎姐，唔駛咁都入佢牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d328dfa77a2a78d616f298bb3f2606cce15a7e9d","tid":2014171,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T00:14:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54b4ce7038469730bcece2f4a4e42c70aa2206a4","tid":2014171,"uid":281417,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T00:15:42.000Z","msg":"懷疑佢哋分開可能因為政治立場唔同"},{"pid":"caab5a3568bec22882ff63692d